<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Connexion | VotreMarque</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Plus+Jakarta+Sans:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary: #7B61FF;
            --primary-dark: #5D47E5;
            --secondary: #FF7D61;
            --dark: #1A1A2E;
            --light: #F8F9FF;
            --gray: #E2E4F0;
            --text-light: #6B7280;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            display: flex;
            min-height: 100vh;
            background-color: var(--light);
            color: var(--dark);
        }
        
        /* Colonne illustration (50%) */
        .auth-illustration {
            width: 50%;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary), var(--primary-dark));
            display: none;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        
        .auth-illustration::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            width: 300px;
            height: 300px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
            top: -100px;
            right: -100px;
        }
        
        .auth-illustration::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            width: 200px;
            height: 200px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
            bottom: -50px;
            left: -50px;
        }
        
        .illustration-content {
            position: absolute;
            top: 50%;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            width: 80%;
            max-width: 500px;
        }
        
        .illustration-content h2 {
            font-size: 2rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            line-height: 1.3;
        }
        
        .illustration-content p {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            opacity: 0.9;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        
        /* Colonne formulaire (50%) */
        .auth-form {
            width: 50%;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 2rem;
            background-color: white;
        }
        
        .form-container {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 400px;
            padding: 0 1.5rem;
        }
        
        .logo {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
        }
        
        .logo svg {
            width: 48px;
            height: 48px;
        }
        
        .logo h1 {
            font-size: 1.75rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--primary);
            margin-top: 1rem;
            margin-bottom: 0;
        }
        
        .form-title {
            font-size: 1.75rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        /* Style des champs */
        .form-group {
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }
        
        .form-control {
            width: 100%;
            height: 52px;
            padding: 0 1.25rem;
            border: 2px solid var(--gray);
            border-radius: 10px;
            font-size: 1rem;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        
        .form-control:focus {
            border-color: var(--primary);
            outline: none;
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px rgba(123, 97, 255, 0.15);
        }
        
        /* Options sous le formulaire */
        .form-options {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            margin: 1.5rem 0;
        }
        
        .remember-me {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }
        
        .remember-me input {
            width: 18px;
            height: 18px;
            margin-right: 0.75rem;
        }
        
        .remember-me label {
            font-size: 0.9375rem;
            color: var(--text-light);
        }
        
        .forgot-password a {
            color: var(--primary);
            font-size: 0.875rem;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        
        /* Bouton principal */
        .btn-primary {
            width: 100%;
            height: 52px;
            background-color: var(--primary);
            color: white;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 10px;
            font-size: 1rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }
        
        .btn-primary:hover {
            background-color: var(--primary-dark);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }
        
        /* Divider */
        .divider {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            margin: 1.5rem 0;
            color: var(--text-light);
            font-size: 0.875rem;
        }
        
        .divider::before,
        .divider::after {
            content: '';
            flex: 1;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--gray);
        }
        
        .divider::before {
            margin-right: 1rem;
        }
        
        .divider::after {
            margin-left: 1rem;
        }
        
        /* Bouton Google */
        .btn-google {
            width: 100%;
            height: 52px;
            background: white;
            color: var(--dark);
            border: 2px solid var(--gray);
            border-radius: 10px;
            font-size: 1rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 0.75rem;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }
        
        .btn-google:hover {
            border-color: var(--primary-light);
        }
        
        /* Lien d'inscription */
        .auth-footer {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 0.9375rem;
            color: var(--text-light);
        }
        
        .auth-footer a {
            color: var(--primary);
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        
        /* Messages */
        .alert {
            padding: 1rem;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .alert-danger {
            background-color: #f8d7da;
            color: #721c24;
            border: 1px solid #f5c6cb;
        }
        
        .alert-info {
            background-color: #e2f4ff;
            color: #0c5460;
            border: 1px solid #bee5eb;
        }
        
        /* Responsive */
        @media (min-width: 992px) {
            .auth-illustration {
                display: flex;
            }
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 991px) {
            body {
                flex-direction: column;
            }
            .auth-illustration, .auth-form {
                width: 100%;
            }
            .auth-illustration {
                height: 200px;
            }
            .illustration-content {
                width: 90%;
            }
            .form-container {
                padding: 0;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <!-- Colonne illustration -->
    <div class="auth-illustration">
        <div class="illustration-content">
            <h2>Content de vous revoir</h2>
            <p>Connectez-vous pour accéder à votre espace personnel et continuer votre expérience.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <!-- Colonne formulaire -->
    <div class="auth-form">
        <div class="form-container">
            
            
            <h1 class="form-title">Connexion</h1>
            
            {% if error %}
                <div class="alert alert-danger">
                    {{ error.messageKey|trans(error.messageData, 'security') }}
                </div>
            {% endif %}
            
            
            <form method="post">
                <div class="form-group">
                    <input 
                        type="email" 
                        value="{{ last_username }}" 
                        name="email" 
                        id="inputEmail" 
                        class="form-control" 
                        placeholder="Adresse email" 
                        required 
                        autofocus
                    >
                </div>
                
                <div class="form-group">
                    <input 
                        type="password" 
                        name="password" 
                        id="inputPassword" 
                        class="form-control" 
                        placeholder="Mot de passe" 
                        required
                    >
                </div>
                
                <div class="form-options">
                    <div class="remember-me">
                        <input type="checkbox" id="remember_me" name="_remember_me">
                        <label for="remember_me">Se souvenir de moi</label>
                    </div>
                    <div class="forgot-password">
                        <a href="{{ path('app_motpsoubl') }}">Mot de passe oublié ?</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <input type="hidden" name="_csrf_token" value="{{ csrf_token('authenticate') }}">
                
                <button type="submit" class="btn-primary">
                    Se connecter
                </button>
            </form>
            
            <div class="divider">
                ou
            </div>
            
            <button class="btn-google">
                <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 18 18" fill="none">
                    <path d="M17.5781 9.20578C17.5781 8.56641 17.5203 7.95312 17.4141 7.36523H9V10.8496H13.8984C13.7355 11.9196 13.166 12.8301 12.2883 13.4414V15.5127H15.0586C16.7719 13.9336 17.5781 11.7715 17.5781 9.20578Z" fill="#4285F4"/>
                    <path d="M9 18C11.25 18 13.1191 17.2266 14.5586 15.9129L11.7883 13.8416C11.0156 14.4117 10.0078 14.7539 9 14.7539C6.87305 14.7539 5.08594 13.3805 4.44141 11.459H1.58203V13.5938C3.02344 16.4531 5.80078 18 9 18Z" fill="#34A853"/>
                    <path d="M4.44141 11.459C4.23047 10.8398 4.11328 10.1754 4.11328 9.48828C4.11328 8.80117 4.23047 8.13672 4.44141 7.51758V5.38281H1.58203C0.878906 6.83203 0.5 8.46875 0.5 10.1133C0.5 11.7578 0.878906 13.3945 1.58203 14.8438L4.44141 12.709C4.23047 12.0898 4.11328 11.4254 4.11328 10.7383C4.11328 10.0512 4.23047 9.38672 4.44141 8.76758V7.51758Z" fill="#FBBC05"/>
                    <path d="M9 4.24219C10.1172 4.24219 11.1328 4.60547 11.9414 5.32031L14.625 2.63672C13.1191 1.23047 11.25 0.410156 9 0.410156C5.80078 0.410156 3.02344 1.95703 1.58203 4.81641L4.44141 6.95117C5.08594 5.02969 6.87305 3.65625 9 3.65625V4.24219Z" fill="#EA4335"/>
                </svg>
                Continuer avec Google
            </button>
            
            <div class="auth-footer">
                Pas encore de compte ? <a href="{{ path('app_register') }}">S'inscrire</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>